                             LEGAL flag HOLIDAYS

In accordance with the official holidays set forth in LA. R.S. 1:55, Section
                                     E,
                    Court will be closed on these dates:

              * New Year's Day - January 1, 2002
              * Martin Luther King's Birthday - January 21, 2002
              * Mardi Gras - February 12, 2002
              * President's Day - February 18, 2002
              * Good Friday - March 29, 2002
              * Memorial Day - May 27, 2002
              * Independence Day - July 4, 2002
              * Labor Day - September 2, 2002
              * All Saint's Day - November 1, 2002
              * Veterans Day - November 11, 2002
              * Thanksgiving - November 28, 2002
              * Friday after Thanksgiving - November 29, 2002
              * Christmas Eve - December 24, 2002
              * Christmas Day - December 25, 2002
              * New Year's Eve - December 31, 2002

